{"tid":441173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果發生依d事，你會點抉擇？","createTime":"2017-10-19T12:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T14:55:29.000Z","uid":141442,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01a92719ef99382951d4747513ceeb9dff1926ff","tid":441173,"uid":141442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"如果有一日你訓醒左，去左第二個平行世界，發現原本你既男朋友/女朋友變左第二個，但佢同你經歷左好多野，亦都好愛你，但係你印象中佢係唔存在。<br />\n<br />\n同時你印象中既男朋友/女朋友返黎搵你，你記得佢亦好愛佢，佢都好愛你，你淨係對佢有印象，對身邊陌生既男朋友/女朋友無印象。<br />\n<br />\n但你所謂既陌生男朋友/女朋友係呢個時間線亦為你付出好多，陪你經歷左好多好多野，愛你愛到爆。<br />\n<br />\n無論簡左邊個，另一個都會好痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n咁你會簡返同陌生既對象一齊，定係熟悉既對象一齊？"},{"pid":"07f9a4e320e3bcdd3c83a4028c5147cd855ed75a","tid":441173,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"靚d果個"},{"pid":"83a0489811438d3ff0400196e6880dc7463c934d","tid":441173,"uid":141442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚d果個</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef06ca3028c00094098b5cfdabc6029aedff12bc","tid":441173,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靚d果個</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記憶係原本個時間線<br />\n應該好難揀個見都未見過既痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b2453337b306ff4ad03945f67c6cf93e764565","tid":441173,"uid":139676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"up乜9"},{"pid":"0b54a256022169cfa1c329c6e997e3e2cf33446a","tid":441173,"uid":64155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"斬撚死你個臭閪咪得囉"},{"pid":"ab6a0a29624cdc4d5878f0566f35399ab1d87978","tid":441173,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被